    • Method Detail

      • rollRandomdrop

        public void rollRandomdrop(double startX,
                           double startY)
        Rolls for a drop and if it does roll positive creates that drop at startX startY. Currently set up to: 30% Bronze coin 10p 20% Silver coin 100p 10% Gold coin 1000p 8% 1 of 4 colored Gems 1500p 2% A heart that gives a life and 1p
        Parameters:
        startX - Start position X
        startY - Start position Y
